title: Miami Dolphins' biggest draft busts of all-time - Sun Sentinel
text:
Miami Dolphins' biggest draft busts of all-time Miami Dolphins all-time biggest draft busts 12. LB Eddie Moore, 2003, Second round ROBERT MAYER / Sun Sentinel 
Eddie Moore over Anquan Boldin? Yes, the Dolphins took the unproductive linebacker in the second round in 2003. After trading away their first-round pick in 2003 for Ricky Williams, Moore was their top selection.
